Does "social distancing" really apply to outdoor events? Or better question is should it? The FF is HUGE and I'm pretty sure it's possible to maintain a 6' distance between people. Besides, the whole "social distancing" thing is a joke. Just go to any Walmart, grocery store, Target or any number of other public places.
**This is my own opinion and in no way reflects the opinions of Cleetus & company.**
The supercharger whine on the redeye was sick!!
